trans-unit.source: Provides a component editor for the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollection"></xref> object in the associated <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Zawiera Edytor składnika <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollection"> </xref> obiektu w skojarzonym <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu"> </xref> formantu.

trans-unit.source: The SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor class provides a user interface for editing the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyle> elements of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollection> object in the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> control at design time, under the control of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuDesigner> object.
trans-unit.target: Klasa SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor udostępnia interfejs użytkownika do edycji <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyle>elementy <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollection>obiektu w skojarzonym <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>formantu w czasie projektowania, pod kontrolą <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuDesigner>obiektu.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuDesigner> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyle>

trans-unit.source: There is a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollection> associated with the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelSubMenuStyles%2A> property of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> control.
trans-unit.target: Brak <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollection>skojarzone z <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelSubMenuStyles%2A>Właściwość <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>kontroli.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelSubMenuStyles%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollection>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollection> object is used to apply styles to static submenu items that depend on their level (nesting depth) in the menu structure.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollection>Obiektu służy do stosowania Style podmenu statycznych elementów, które są zależne od ich poziomu (głębokości zagnieżdżania) w strukturze menu.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollection>

trans-unit.source: The SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor is invoked, for example, by selecting the ellipsis button (**…**) on the **LevelSubMenuStyles** row in the **Properties** grid of the visual designer.
trans-unit.target: SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor zostanie wywołany, na przykład, klikając przycisk wielokropka (**... **) na **LevelSubMenuStyles** wierszu w **właściwości** siatki projektanta wizualnego.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor.CanSelectMultipleInstances%2A> method always returns `false` to indicate that only one object can be selected at a time in the editor.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor.CanSelectMultipleInstances%2A>Metoda zawsze zwraca `false` aby wskazać, że tylko jeden obiekt można wybrać w czasie w edytorze.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor.CanSelectMultipleInstances%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor.CreateCollectionForm%2A> method creates a new form to display and edit the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollection>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor.CreateCollectionForm%2A>Metoda tworzy nowy formularz, aby wyświetlić i edytować <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollection>.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor.CreateCollectionForm%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor.CreateInstance%2A> method creates a new instance of the specified collection item type.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor.CreateInstance%2A>Metoda tworzy nowe wystąpienie typu elementu w określonej kolekcji.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor.CreateInstance%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor.CreateNewItemTypes%2A> method returns an array of types that the editor can create.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor.CreateNewItemTypes%2A>Metoda zwraca tablicę typów, które można utworzyć w edytorze.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor.CreateNewItemTypes%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicjuje nowe wystąpienie klasy <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor"> </xref> klasy.

trans-unit.source: The .NET Framework internally constructs a new instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor> class when you select, for example, the ellipsis button (**…**) on the **LevelSubMenuStyles** row in the **Properties** grid of the visual designer when designing a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> control or a control that is derived from the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> class.
trans-unit.target: .NET Framework wewnętrznie tworzy nowe wystąpienie klasy <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor>Po wybraniu, na przykład przycisk wielokropka (**... **) na **LevelSubMenuStyles** wierszu w **właściwości** siatki projektanta podczas projektowania <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>formantu lub kontrolkę, która jest pochodną <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>klasy</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Type> of the collection to edit.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Type>Kolekcji do edycji.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether multiple <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyle"></xref> elements can be selected in the editor at one time.
trans-unit.target: Pobiera wartość wskazującą czy wiele <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyle"> </xref> elementów można wybrać w edytorze w tym samym czasie.

trans-unit.source: The CanSelectMultipleInstances method always returns `false`; thus, only one <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyle> object can be selected at a time in the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor> object.
trans-unit.target: Metoda CanSelectMultipleInstances zawsze zwraca `false`; w związku z tym tylko jeden <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyle>w danym momencie można wybrać obiektu <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor>obiektu.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyle>
